OL,3,CRising number of single women
OL,4,Cundergoing IVF, regulator finds
OL,6,FThe number of single women having in-
OL,7,Fvitro fertilisation (IVF) treatment is
OL,8,Fon the rise, according to figures from
OL,9,Fthe UK's fertility regulator.
OL,11,FBetween 2012 and 2022, the proportion
OL,12,Fof IVF cycles being carried out for
OL,13,Fsingle women trebled, up from 2% of
OL,14,Fall treatments to 6%.
OL,16,FThe total number of single women
OL,17,Fhaving IVF or donor insemination
OL,18,Ftreatment was over three times higher
OL,19,Fin 2022 than in 2012, increasing from
OL,20,F1,400 to 4,800.
