OL,3,CRising number of single women
OL,4,Cundergoing IVF, regulator finds
OL,6,FThe figures come from a report by the
OL,7,FHuman Fertilisation and Embryology
OL,8,FAuthority (HFEA), which also found
OL,9,Fsingle women and lesbian couples had
OL,10,Fthe highest birth rates after
OL,11,Fundergoing IVF treatment.
OL,13,FHowever, less than a fifth of single
OL,14,Fwomen and lesbians received NHS
OL,15,Ffunding for their first IVF treatment,
OL,16,Fcompared to 52% of heterosexual
OL,17,Fcouples between the ages of 18 and 39.
