OL,3,CRising number of single women
OL,4,Cundergoing IVF, regulator finds
OL,6,FSimon Blake, chief executive of
OL,7,FStonewall, said LGBTQ+ people continue
OL,8,Fto face financial barriers to
OL,9,Faccessing fertility treatment.
OL,11,FHe said: "Unlike for heterosexual
OL,12,Fcouples, 90% of integrated health care
OL,13,Fboards in England require LGBTQ plus
OL,14,Fcouples to self-fund at least six
OL,15,Fcycles of artificial insemination
OL,16,Fbefore they are eligible for NHS IVF
OL,17,Ftreatment.
