OL,6,F"This is simply unaffordable for many
OL,7,Fand means LGBTQ plus couples are often
OL,8,Funable to start a family. Urgent
OL,9,Fchange is needed so all people who
OL,10,Fwant children have the same access to
OL,11,Fservices, and their sexuality does not
OL,12,Fdetermine the choices available to
OL,13,Fthem."
OL,15,FJulia Chain, chairwoman of the HFEA,
OL,16,Furged commissioners of fertility
OL,17,Fservices to review whether existing
OL,18,Feligibility criteria is negatively
OL,19,Fimpacting people's access to treatment.
