OL,6,FOnly one in ten egg freezing
OL,7,Ftreatments were among heterosexual
OL,8,Fcouples, but this group was more
OL,9,Flikely to thaw eggs for treatment
OL,10,Fcompared with single women, it said.
OL,12,FFor the first time, the report also
OL,13,Fhighlights the proportion of families
OL,14,Fwho are using surrogacy. In 2022,
OL,15,Fheterosexual couples accounted for 39%
OL,16,Fof surrogacy cycles, with "other
OL,17,Ffamily types" making up the other 61%.
